2 Release build
***************

After git clone, build the Debian package with one command (installs
build deps via ‘sudo apt-get’ when needed):

     ./build.sh

   Full release (Docker push + deb), version from ‘pyproject.toml’
unless passed explicitly:

     ./scripts/release_build.sh
     ./scripts/release_build.sh 1.0.7 --deb-only

   Environment variables:

‘CASMGR_DOCKER_REGISTRY’
     Docker Hub user or registry prefix (default: ‘vasilyvz’).
‘CASMGR_DOCKER_IMAGE_NAME’
     Image name (default: ‘casmgr-postgres’).

   Flags:

‘--deb-only’
     Build the Debian package without pushing Docker.
‘--docker-only’
     Push Docker only, skip ‘dpkg-buildpackage’.
‘--skip-deps’
     Do not auto-install build packages.


