11 Systemd
**********

‘casmgr-postgres.service’
     Oneshot unit: starts Docker container via
     ‘casmgr-postgres-container start’.  Requires Docker.
‘casmgr-server.service’
     Runs ‘python -m code_analysis.main --config /etc/casmgr/config.json
     --daemon’ as ‘casuser’.  Requires ‘casmgr-postgres.service’.  Loads
     ‘/var/casmgr/secrets/.env’.

     sudo systemctl enable casmgr-postgres casmgr-server
     sudo systemctl start casmgr-postgres
     sudo casmgr-pg-init
     sudo systemctl start casmgr-server
     sudo systemctl status casmgr-postgres casmgr-server
     sudo systemctl restart casmgr-server
     sudo journalctl -u casmgr-server -f

   The package starts ‘casmgr-server’ automatically only when config has
no ‘CHANGE_ME’ or ‘MCP_PROXY_HOST’ placeholders and all five mTLS files
exist.


