12 Environment
**************

Admin scripts and services honor these variables when set:

‘CASMGR_CONFIG’
     Path to ‘config.json’ (default ‘/etc/casmgr/config.json’).
‘CASMGR_SECRETS’
     Secrets directory (default ‘/var/casmgr/secrets’).
‘CASMGR_ETC’, ‘CASMGR_VAR’, ‘CASMGR_LOG’
     Configuration, data, and log roots under FHS layout.
‘CASMGR_PG_CONTAINER’
     Docker container name (default ‘casmgr-postgres’).
‘CASMGR_DOCKER_IMAGE_FILE’
     Pinned image ref (default ‘/usr/share/casmgr/docker-image’).
‘CODE_ANALYSIS_DAEMON_PYTHON’, ‘CASMGR_PYTHON’
     Override Python interpreter for admin tooling.


